      "id": "PopularPost47371",
      "post_content": "I love the clay-mation look of the original art. Functionally, Drudge Skeletons are excellent blockers. Second only to [Will-o'-the-Wisps](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Will-o'-the-Wisps) in terms of casting cost and ability to block. The skeletons can take a hit from an [Earth Elemental](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Earth Elemental) or [Craw Wurm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Craw Wurm), pick up their bones, and be around next turn to block all over again. The casting cost is low, so these guys can come out early and buy you some time while you build up your mana base for bigger creatures like [Sengir Vampire](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sengir Vampire) or [Nightmare](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nightmare).",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost47371\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">I love the clay-mation look of the original art.  Functionally, Drudge Skeletons are excellent blockers.  Second only to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Will-o'-the-Wisps\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Will-o'-the-Wisps\">Will-o'-the-Wisps</a> in terms of casting cost and ability to block.  The skeletons can take a hit from an <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Earth Elemental\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Earth Elemental\">Earth Elemental</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Craw Wurm\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Craw Wurm\">Craw Wurm</a>, pick up their bones, and be around next turn to block all over again.  The casting cost is low, so these guys can come out early and buy you some time while you build up your mana base for bigger creatures like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sengir Vampire\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sengir Vampire\">Sengir Vampire</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Nightmare\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nightmare\">Nightmare</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '47371'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\