      "id": "PopularPost119107",
      "post_content": "The original skeleton! I cannot overstate how much I like these guys. They were one of the first *misinterpreted* cards I liked to play with - between the flavour text and a fast and loose understanding of the rules, I originally thought that these guys could come back from the graveyard for ![Black](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=B&type=symbol)! It didn't take long before we realized how stupidly strong that would be, although with [Reassembling Skeleton](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reassembling Skeleton) WotC has printed something quite close. =)\n  \n   \n@Eppek - totally agree re: the art. ",
      "posted_by": "Leshrac_Nightwalker",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost119107\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">The original skeleton!  I cannot overstate how much I like these guys.  They were one of the first <i>misinterpreted</i> cards I liked to play with - between the flavour text and a fast and loose understanding of the rules, I originally thought that these guys could come back from the graveyard for <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Black\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=B&amp;type=symbol\"/>!  It didn't take long before we realized how stupidly strong that would be, although with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Reassembling Skeleton\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reassembling Skeleton\">Reassembling Skeleton</a> WotC has printed something quite close.  =)  \r<br/> <br/>@Eppek - totally agree re: the art.  </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '119107'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2435\">Leshrac_Nightwalker</span>\r\n                                (11/30/2010 10:02:30 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;